cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with person re-identification, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a deep learning model for this task, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. The paper also involves attention mechanisms, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), and the proposed model is capable of producing dynamic representations, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with similarity measuring, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
